            We're delighted that you're considering sharing Voy with the people you know! Our refer-a-friend programme is our way of saying thank you for spreading the word about your weight loss journey and our service. Here's how it works:
For your friend

For you
You'll earn a discount on your next order based on how many friends you refer:

One or two friends: 30% off your next order
Three or more friends: 60% off your next order

How to refer a friend

Log into your Voy account

            Question: How do I refer a friend?

            Answer:

response.text:

2.  Go to your "Refer a Friend" page (top right corner of your account).

Starting at a Higher Dose

Confirm the last dose you injected and when you last took your medication

ID
